<p>
MODULA-3 INTERFACES FOR ACCESSING DATABASES
</p>
<p>
   This package contains a "DB" interface and a set of implementations
   for accessing relational databases. 
</p>
<p>
   DB is the safe Modula-3 interface for relational databases.  It
   defines two primary abstractions: database connections and
   statements.
</p>
<p>
   Actual implementations supported are odbc, mysql, postgres95, postgresql.
</p>
